data.description: Well maintained, immaculate 4 Bedroom plus bonus room, 2.5 bath home with large fenced in back yard. New fortified roof 12/20, certificate in documents. Plantation shutters throughout.  Concrete coating in garage and back porch. This coveted subdivision has a pool, tennis courts, half a basketball court and golf putting green.  One owner. Home has exterior lights with timer. Minutes from the Interstate, downtown Fairhope and near the beaches of of Alabama.
